⟨, iz, di⟩ daytshn hobn genumen mener yunge,

575
00:28:23,472 --> 00:28:24,802
kedey zey zoln

576
00:28:25,112 --> 00:28:29,547
min-, di, m- zukhn mines, ober nit v- nit vi me zukht mit metal,

577
00:28:29,547 --> 00:28:31,153
nor mit di eygene kerpers.

578
00:28:30,945 --> 00:28:31,652
yo.

579
00:28:31,153 --> 00:28:32,430
zey zaynen gegangen,

580
00:28:33,094 --> 00:28:34,910
ver es iz aroyf oyf a mine,

581
00:28:35,102 --> 00:28:37,579
un zey hobn oysminirt dem gantsn feld

582
00:28:37,579 --> 00:28:39,252
mit di eygene kerpers.

583
00:28:39,252 --> 00:28:41,080
ot dos iz geven STRASSENHOF.

584
00:28:41,869 --> 00:28:44,934
vifl mentshn s'iz geven in STRASSENHOF? ven bistu gekumen?

585
00:28:44,552 --> 00:28:50,758
ikh bin gekumen ahin, VOT in ende september, nokh der likvidatsye fun Vilner geto. a por teg zaynen mir geven in KAISERWALD.

586
00:28:50,758 --> 00:28:53,338
zaynen mir gekumen, umgefer iz dos geven

587
00:28:53,462 --> 00:28:54,620
ende,

588
00:28:54,880 --> 00:28:56,927
 september dray un fertsik

589
00:28:56,927 --> 00:28:59,194
biz oygust, avgust fir un fertsik.

590
00:28:59,605 --> 00:29:03,008
Vilne iz shoyn geven bafrayt. Vilne hot men bafrayt dem tsvelftn yuli.

591
00:29:03,402 --> 00:29:05,726
mir hobn dos gevust, vayle mir hobn gearbet...

592
00:29:05,726 --> 00:29:11,929
fun onfang hob ikh gearbet als ⟨boy-arbeterke⟩, un nokh dem hob ikh gearbet in a, fabrik. kh'hob ge-,

593
00:29:11,929 --> 00:29:16,508
⟨o- oyf, in i-⟩ dan hob ikh ⟨shoyn in⟩ rusish ongeshribn a, a, a, a lidele. gevebt shtof.

594
00:29:17,391 --> 00:29:19,523
neyn. ikh hob d- ⟨oh⟩, dortn zaynen geven oykh,

595
00:29:19,523 --> 00:29:22,472
mir, STRASSENHOFer yidn,

596
00:29:22,472 --> 00:29:23,488
 himen.

597
00:29:23,488 --> 00:29:29,091
 "mir zaynen di STRASSENHOFer yidn. dos naye Eyrope boyen mir. di arbet vos mir hobn iz farshidn,

598
00:29:29,091 --> 00:29:33,745
ober tsores hobn mir gor on a shir. oy, STRASSENHOF, oy, biz tsum haldz bistu mir.

599
00:29:33,745 --> 00:29:36,254
oy, STRASSENHOF, vi vert men poter shoyn fun dir?

600
00:29:36,173 --> 00:29:36,772
UNK

601
00:29:36,254 --> 00:29:40,403
oy, STRASSENHOF, ven vet shoyn kumen di tsayt az mir veln zayn bafrayt?"

602
00:29:42,532 --> 00:29:44,841
 dertsu hob ikh dortn,

603
00:29:45,673 --> 00:29:46,747
eyn mol,

604
00:29:47,040 --> 00:29:48,809
, oh, s'iz geven dortn aza ⟨HANS⟩,

605
00:29:48,809 --> 00:29:51,861
mit vo-, g- di same shreklekhste shtrof iz geven

606
00:29:52,153 --> 00:29:53,176
shpringen.

607
00:29:54,432 --> 00:29:56,029
shpringen vi fresh.

608
00:29:56,119 --> 00:29:57,311
dos iz shreklekh.

609
00:29:58,127 --> 00:30:00,078
f- mir, mir flegn khaleshn. ah?

610
00:29:58,834 --> 00:29:59,984
borves?

611
00:29:59,984 --> 00:30:00,874
borves?

612
00:30:00,642 --> 00:30:06,504
 nit, nit borves. mir ⟨zaynen, mir hobn⟩ shoyn gehat, oyf, oyf holts zaynen geven, vayl undzere iz shoyn alts geven tserisn,

613
00:30:06,504 --> 00:30:07,330
nor

